Requirements :Linux (debian - ubuntu)
=====================================

apt-get install git ocaml ocaml-compiler-libs caml4p-extra

Requirements: MacOSX 
====================

TBA

Opam code installation and signpostd dependency 
===============================================

> git clone git://github.com/OCamlPro/opam.git

> cd opam/

> make ; make install

> eval `opam config -env`

> opam init 

> opam switch 3.12.1

> opam remote -kind git -add signpostd git://github.com/crotsos/opam-repo-dev.git

> opam install ssl oasis signpostd # this is to get the required libraries. 

